ce for discerning travelers seeking the very best. </p><p>With its ultra-comfortable Guestrooms, cozy Living Room, the exciting new Morgans New York Bar, and the wildly popular Asia de Cuba restaurant, Morgans has earned its reputation as a New York City classic.</p><ul><H3>Come Stay at the Morgans New York, NY Hotel Located at</H3>    <li class="address">MORGANS HOTEL</li>    <li class="address"><GEO TYPE="US">237 Madison Ave New York, New York 10016</GEO></li>    <li class="address">Tel. 212 686 0300 Fax 212 779 8352</li>    <li class="address">Reservations US 800 697 1791</li>    <li class="address">Reservations International 00800 4969 1780</li></ul><p class="morgans">With its ultra-comfortable <a href="http://www.morganshotel.com/morgans_hotel_rooms.asp" title="View the Hotel rooms at Morgans New York">Hotel Guestrooms</a>, cozy <a href="http://www.morganshotel.com/morgans_hotel_living_room.asp" title="View the Living Room at Morgans New York Hotel">Living Room</a>, the exciting new <a href="http://www.morganshotel.com/morgans_hotel_morgans_bar.asp" title="View Morgans Hotel Bar at Morgans Hotel New York">Morgans Hotel Bar</a>, and the wildly popular <a href="http://www.morganshotel.com/morgans_hotel_asia_de_cuba.asp" title="Asia de Cuba restaurant New York Restaurant">Asia de Cuba</a> restaurant, Morgans has earned its reputation as a New York classic.</p></noscript><div id="lowerhomenav"><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="8" width="5" /><br /><div class="homenav"><span class="nav"><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com"><img src="images/MHGgray.gif" alt="Morgans Hotel Group" width="180" height="12" border="0"/></a><br /><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="3" width="5" /><br /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com" title="Morgans Hotel Group Home Page">Home</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/reserve.asp" title="Online Reservations">Reservation